  "title": "Hits: escapeHits should happen after transformItems",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\n\r\nIf a transformItems which modifies `_highlightResult` in a way which makes it fail the regex to give classes is used, it will not apply the regex anymore\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/kxvqkx7j5v?module=%2Fsrc%2Fapp.js\r\n\r\nworkaround needed for now: \r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/2vwml193j?module=%2Fsrc%2Fapp.js\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\n\r\nElements are already escaped and transformed, __before__ transformItems.\r\n\r\n**Environment:**\r\n\r\n - Version: 2.10.3",
